errors.statement:
// They said yes to the offer — now I run the organizer tasklist with all the material.
// The organizer owns the complete build: inventories independently-owned scopes, builds every grounded specialist,
// then hands the complete source to the live-project builder. I pass ALL attachment ids plus the voice-memo facts
// (which only I could transcribe — the builder cannot hear audio) and the image summary (builder cannot see images).

await tasklist('organize_material', {
  request: 'Organize the user\'s entire Tanzania trip into a single app they can open on their phone. They have scattered material: notes with flight details and route, a cost spreadsheet, a park-fee PDF, a Stone Town photo, and a voice memo from Ngorongoro crater. Build per-topic specialist spaces for the distinct parts (flights, safari/Ngorongoro, Zanzibar/Stone Town, costs), then build the live-project app with tables seeded from all provided data, pages for each section, and the photo included.',
  sourceSummary: 'Three files: tanzaniamemories.md (full trip notes with confirmed flights, route, contacts), trip-costs.xlsx (cost spreadsheet), ngorongoro-conservation-area-tariffs.pdf (official park fees). One image: stone-town-zanzibar.jpg (bright white building with dark wooden balconies, Zanzibar light). One voice memo: Ngorongoro crater day — guide named Emmanuel, bought two beaded bracelets for Athina Mari from a Maasai lady at the rim for ~TZS 35,000 (roughly $20-25), Emmanuel mentioned an extra ranger tip of ~TZS 5,000 cash at the gate separate from park fees, need to ask Richard about it before safari balance payment.',
  attachmentIds: ['0a445eb7-663d-4e2a-a097-25a936f7c6dd', '65cc1516-df5f-4c3e-812a-c23ee3e1f495', '98ca16a0-1c86-4758-ad14-14d5e05d35a8', '2382468c-bdc9-4129-a417-063d401b299c'],
  specialistFacts: 'Voice memo (transcribed, not in any file): Guide Emmanuel at Ngorongoro crater (not Richard from the office). Bought two beaded bracelets for Athina Mari from a Maasai lady at the crater rim, paid roughly TZS 35,000 (roughly $20-25). Emmanuel mentioned an extra ranger tip expected at the gate: ~TZS 5,000 cash, separate from park fees. Need to remember to ask Richard about this before the safari balance payment. Image (Stone Town): bright white multi-storey building with dark wooden balconies and arched windows, quiet courtyard view, no people visible — classic Zanzibar architecture.',
}).then((organized) => display(
  organized.ok
    ? 'Everything is organized and ready to open. You now have a single place on your phone with your flights, costs, park fees, the Stone Town photo, and all the loose ends — including that ranger tip to ask Richard about. Open it at /app/' + (projectFiles.find((f: string) => f.endsWith('.project'))?.replace('.project', '') ?? 'your-project') + ' — everything is in one place now.'
    : 'I organized what I could, but part of the setup needs another look. The good news: your files are read and the core structure is in place. Want me to take another pass at whatever did not land?',
));
